{"tid":652457,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[藝術] 欣澳站、迪士尼站同迪士尼綫個設計其實真係世界級","createTime":"2018-05-04T00:24:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T03:38:08.000Z","uid":147226,"like":9,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2478f50d323a309d0d161b541345e8444dbedd97","tid":652457,"uid":147226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T00:24:10.000Z","msg":"老老實實嗰啲咩全世界最靚火車站，好多只係將啲九唔搭八藝術品砌埋一齊，或者啲顏色亂堆砌埋一齊。<br />\n<br />\n但迪士尼綫兩個站同架車真係世界級設計：<br />\n<br />\n欣澳站<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/075339_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F075339_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=6639b191&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/075427_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F075427_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f99006d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好有日本二、三線城市車站 feel，主線中間特急唔停站，然後側邊月台停站，有條橋通去另一個單線月台。<br />\n顏色唔會大紅大紫，但又唔覺好單調，仲有啲樹。<br />\n<br />\n迪士尼站<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/080231_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F080231_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=4e3c864d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n設計簡簡單單，仿上一世紀啲西式建築，成本肯定平過而家用大量玻璃幕牆啲建築物，但簡單得來每一元素都互相配合，唔會有種寒酸感覺。<br />\n<br />\n迪士尼綫<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/080837_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F080837_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=882f1f5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/080842_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F080842_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=a710f30a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n主題列車來講，個設計完全拍得住日本收你幾萬蚊搭幾日果啲，顏色同迪士尼樂園夾之外，仲同返地鐵本身啲車夾。<br />\n無人駕駛列車，所以可以睇車前展望，比較可惜係沿線無咩風景。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後貼啲所謂世界最靚啲車站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完全唔識欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/081313_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F081313_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=b15b604a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/081841_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F081841_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=6e717cca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/082212_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F082212_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=60274eb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/082332_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F082332_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=be36b7d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c90b0f5588ff2bbd90aca6b7357a08988ec04a9e","tid":652457,"uid":43924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T03:30:07.000Z","msg":"港鐵？不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d27fcc69641f9ecc4e78229f360f9d2a5aeff2c2","tid":652457,"uid":48675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T03:33:28.000Z","msg":"夏天熱撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fe1726cd5aec444129d3a88358f39dd980636f3","tid":652457,"uid":179467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T03:37:10.000Z","msg":"其實欣澳站兩隻波口都唔係高速道岔,唔可以俾機場快線車唔減速係135過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ce8c4b824b387d56100b4b450f4614d52f7a373","tid":652457,"uid":179467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T03:38:08.000Z","msg":"btw高捷美麗島站個設計,我都覺得係唔識欣賞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}